{
  "stem": "27507.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went with [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my father, my cousin Jurek, who was then a young boy, a teenager-- he was maybe 17 or 18, something like that-- and myself.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- How long did you stay in Bialystok altogether?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Altogether, about six months, I think, because that was in early April.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was like in '40.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was '40, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of course, the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The beginning of the war was September--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we wandered around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we came to Bialystok probably in November.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed there through the winter, '39/'40.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was probably in April 1940.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how it was organized exactly that we were-- that we managed to go to cross over to Warsaw I'm not quite sure.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there were-- there was a whole organized chain of people who must have been paid and who helped us to cross that border.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- and it was, of course, we couldn't use any official means of transport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, it was not so far to the border, because Warsaw to Bialystok is maybe 150 kilometers, so to the border it must have been, oh, maybe a bit more.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But maybe it was 80 kilometers, something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were traveling on peasants'-- on peasants' carts and basically peasants' clothing or more or less-- well, everybody was dressed in remnants of what they had of their old clothing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And whenever it came to a little village or a town where there was a danger that we would--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--come across the police or soldiers, we would then walk all around and walk in the fields to avoid any-- any town.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we passed in one place where there was a market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we slept in peasants' houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
